subsection.def:
land
                    (土地) does not include incorporeal
                hereditaments;

benefit
                    (利益) means any financial or proprietary gain,
                whether temporary or permanent;

gain
                    (獲益) includes a gain by keeping what one has,
                as well as a gain by getting what one has not;

loss
                    (損失) includes a loss by not getting what one
                might get, as well as a loss by parting with what one has;

deception
                    (欺騙手段) has the same meaning as in
                    section 17;

